These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, animation, musical, family, thriller, zombie
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: soul, classical, funk, country, metal, hip-hop
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, roller, ship, taxi, train
 1. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the fan of classical is the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is the fan of soul##1
 5. the person watching action movies is the fan of metal##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
10. the person watching action movies is between the person driving the ship and the person watching animation movies##2
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
13. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the ship is the fan of classical##1
15. the fan of classical is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |   5    |   6   |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie | animation  | action | musical      | thriller   | family |
| Music-Genre   | country  | soul  | metal    | classical | hip-hop | funk |
| Transport     | jet-ski   | airplane | train     | ship      | roller | taxi  |

