.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: lavender, grey, green, chestnut, ebony, mauve
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: d&b, trance, house, disco, folk, punk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, tennis, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
 3. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of punk##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is the fan of d&b##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 9. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
11. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
12. the fan of disco is the person who likes grey##1
13. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
14. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who likes ebony##1
15. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes green##1
16. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
17. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |     3      |    4     |      5      |     6      |
| Color    | green          | mauve  | lavender     | grey | ebony | chestnut       |
| Music-Genre   | punk | d&b | trance | disco  | folk  | house    |
| Sport   | baseball      | water-polo  | ice-hockey | cricket  | tennis      | basketball |

