 2. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 9. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
10. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of metal##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
13. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
14. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1

