.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, march, september, january, february, april
6 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, mouse, goat, rabbit, hamster
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, parkour, swimming, april-polo
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
10. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's sport is april-polo##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
12. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is april-polo##1
13. the person who's sport is april-polo is the owner of the goat##1
14. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
15. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
16. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| Birthday      | april      | september | january | november        | march   | february     |
| Pet   | ferret | rabbit         | lizard   | hamster       | mouse     | goat     |
| Sport         | parkour    | cricket       | golf  | basketball | swimming | april-polo |

