.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-3-6::.
There 6 different types of food: banana, carrot, grapes, papaya, peach, pepper
House: wooden, tower, cottage, gothic-revival, modern, art-deco
There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, australian, indonesian, argentine, thai, chinese
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the tower house##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 3. the argentine is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person eating papaya is between the person eating pepper and the australian##2
 5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
 7. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the thai##3
 8. the tower house is the person eating papaya##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the australian##1
11. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
12. the person eating pepper is on the right of the modern house##1
13. the person eating pepper is the mexican##1
14. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |      3      |    4    |       5        |      6       |
| Food          | carrot             | pepper     | papaya      | grapes  | peach          | banana       |
| House           | modern | cottage | tower | art-deco | gothic-revival | wooden         |
