 1. the owner of the rabbit is the indian##1
 2. the townhouse house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 5. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 8. the craftsman house is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the german##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
11. the townhouse house is on the left of the german##1
12. the australian is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
13. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the canadian##3
14. the owner of the goldfish is between the mexican and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |     5      |       6        |
