 8. the person who's sport is climbing is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
11. the hamburgerman-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
