 2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is between the person playing billiard and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the person who growstulip is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person playing canasta is the person who growsdahlia##1
13. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
14. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |     5     |      6      |
| Beverage   | tea      | fanta       | cola       | coffee     | sprite    | almond-milk |
| Game       | canasta | whist      | mah-jongg    | billiard      | go | bridge  |
| Flower      | dahlia  | lily | amaryllis | tulip | azalea   | balloon-flower     |

